        {
            "title": "橋水旗艦宏觀對沖基金飆升26% 勢創2010年以來最佳表現",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 橋水的旗艦宏觀基金今年前九個月上漲26.4%，關稅引發的市場不確定性提振該公司及其同行的表現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一位知情人士稱，該對沖基金邁向2010年以來最大上漲。這位知情人士因回報數據非公開而不願具名。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對沖基金今年整體表現強勁，得益於美國股市飆升和美國總統川普的貿易戰引發債匯市場大幅波動。標普500指數前三季度上漲14%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">過去十年對橋水和其他宏觀基金而言並不輕鬆，利率處於歷史性低位，導致市場波動下降，而波動正是這些基金獲取收益的來源。橋水的Pure Alpha II宏觀基金在2012至2024年間的年化回報率不到3%。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0d5448e3-3a02-3a0c-a99f-438252d13dc3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">橋水發言人拒絕對近期回報發表評論。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至9月，橋水的亞洲總回報(Asia Total Return)基金上漲32%，中國總回報(China Total Return)基金上漲28.9%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至12月31日，橋水資產管理規模為920億美元，低於2023年初的近1,400億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Bridgewater Soars 26% to Lead Pack of Biggest Hedge Funds</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Hema Parmar.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A9%8B%E6%B0%B4%E6%97%97%E8%89%A6%E5%AE%8F%E8%A7%80%E5%B0%8D%E6%B2%96%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%8726-%E5%8B%A2%E5%89%B52010%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE-222205867.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-03 07:00:49",
